# Project Development Phase

## Project Development Phase

The Project Development phase involves building and integrating all the components of the AI-Powered Lead Generation System. During this phase, Salesforce CRM, Agentforce, Apex, and Salesforce Flow were configured to automate lead generation, lead scoring, and sales recommendations.

### Development Objectives

* Develop a Salesforce-based lead management system.
* Integrate AI and Agentforce for lead prediction and prioritization.
* Automate business processes using Salesforce Flow.
* Create reports and dashboards for sales monitoring.
* Ensure secure and efficient management of customer data.

### Development Process

#### 1. Salesforce Setup

* Created a Salesforce Developer Organization.
* Configured users, profiles, and permissions.
* Set up the required Salesforce environment.

#### 2. Data Model Development

* Created custom objects and fields to store lead information.
* Defined relationships between objects.
* Configured validation rules to ensure accurate data entry.

#### 3. User Interface Development

* Designed Lightning record pages for lead management.
* Configured page layouts and navigation for easy access.
* Developed user-friendly forms for creating and updating leads.

#### 4. AI and Agentforce Integration

* Configured Agentforce to analyze lead data.
* Implemented AI-based lead scoring and conversion prediction.
* Generated intelligent recommendations for sales representatives.

#### 5. Workflow Automation

* Developed Salesforce Flows to automate:

  * Lead assignment.
  * Follow-up task creation.
  * Notifications and alerts.
  * Lead status updates.

#### 6. Apex Development

* Developed Apex classes and triggers to implement business logic.
* Automated record updates and validations.
* Improved system functionality where declarative tools were not sufficient.

#### 7. Reports and Dashboards

* Created reports to monitor lead status and conversion rates.
* Designed dashboards for sales managers to track team performance and business insights.

### Development Tools

* Salesforce CRM
* Salesforce Agentforce
* Salesforce Flow
* Apex Programming Language
* Lightning App Builder
* Reports & Dashboards

### Development Outcome

The development phase resulted in a fully functional AI-Powered Lead Generation System capable of collecting lead information, predicting lead conversion, prioritizing leads, automating follow-up activities, and providing real-time business insights. The system improves sales efficiency by enabling teams to focus on high-potential leads and make data-driven decisions.
